ygData.messageBody:
Greetings,

In regard to faction with the corrupt guards killing
orcs won't help... you have to run quests for the
Rogue guild to start with and then later quest for the
corrupt milita to increase flavor with them... you
have to use the secret tunnels to get into freeport to
do the quests though... There are 2 tunnels located
around the west gate... look around or ask someone...
its too hard to explain in this manner!

Be well,

Len Yong
16th Monk
Bertoxxulous Server
